All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
DocumentBuilder
The DocumentBuilder interface defines methods for creating and managing documents that contain test case information.
Extractor
The Extractor class provides functionality for extracting secondary zip files from a main zip file and saving them to a specified destination directory.
FileDeleter
The FileDeleter class provides functionality for deleting a list of files.
Flight
The Flight class is supposed to be extracted from student submissions but I just used this sample one for now to generate the javadoc
FlightTest
The FlightTest class contains JUnit test methods for testing the functionality of the Flight class.
JavaPackageInserter
The JavaPackageInserter class provides functionality to add a package declaration to a Java file if it is missing.
LuggageManifest
The LuggageManifest class is supposed to be extracted from student submissions but I just used this sample one for now to generate the javadoc
LuggageManifestTest
The LuggageManifestTest class contains test cases for the `LuggageManifest` class.
LuggageSlip
The LuggageSlip class is supposed to be extracted from student submissions but I just used this sample one for now to generate the javadoc
LuggageSlipTest
The LuggageSlipTest class contains test cases for the `LuggageSlip` class.
Main
The Main class serves as the entry point for the project.
MarksAwarded
The MarksAwarded class is responsible for calculating and retrieving the total marks awarded for various test interfaces related to passenger, flight, luggage slip, and luggage manifest.
Passenger
The Passenger class is supposed to be extracted from student submissions but I just used this sample one for now to generate the javadoc
PassengerTest
The PassengerTest class contains test cases to validate the functionality of the Passenger class.
PDFGenerator
PDFGenerator class responsible for creating a PDF document summarizing the test cases' results.
ProjectManager
The ProjectManager class orchestrates the processing of student submissions.
SubmissionProcessor
The SubmissionProcessor class handles the processing of student submissions.
TestCase
The TestCase class represents a test case with a name, status, and feedback.
TestInterface
The TestInterface interface defines a method to retrieve marks.
TestSuite
The TestSuite class serves as a JUnit test suite for running multiple test classes and generating a PDF document summarizing the test results.
